                            <comment id="14902035" author="anshumg" created="Tue, 22 Sep 2015 06:28:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;That must&apos;ve been accidental (keyboard shortcut). But, I was actually thinking of removing that as it still affects only 5.3 and might be fixed with 5.4.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That&apos;s been my interpretation of the affected versions field, but I could be wrong there. I generally only add already released versions in the list of &apos;affected versions&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll add that back and if this gets fixed in time for 5.4, we could always remove 5.4 from there again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
